### Bubble Game
A fun and simple bubble popping game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

#Features
Random Bubble Generation: Bubbles with random numbers appear on the screen.
Timer and Score: The game includes a countdown timer and keeps track of your score based on correct clicks.
Interactive Gameplay: Click the correct bubble to earn points before the timer runs out.

##How to Play
Start the game and watch the bubbles appear.
Click on the bubble with the number shown in the "Hit" box.
Earn points for each correct bubble before time runs out.

##Technologies Used
      -HTML for structure
      -CSS for styling
      -JavaScript for game logic and interactivity

###Purpose
This project was created as part of my JavaScript learning journey to practice DOM manipulation and event handling.
